<form action="" method="post" class="form-horizontal">
    <fieldset>
        <!-- Form Name -->
        <legend>Ödeme Linki Oluştur</legend>

        <!-- Text input-->
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for="">Müşteri Adı (*):</label>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <input
                    name="name"
                    type="text"
                    value="Fatih"
                    class="form-control input-md"
                    required
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for="">Müşteri Soyadı (*):</label>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <input
                    name="surname"
                    type="text"
                    value="Coskun"
                    class="form-control input-md"
                    required
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for="">Müşteri TCKN (Opsiyonel):</label>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <input
                    name="tcCertificate"
                    type="text"
                    value=""
                    class="form-control input-md"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for=""
                >Müşteri Vergi No (Opsiyonel):</label
            >
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <input
                    name="taxNumber"
                    type="text"
                    value=""
                    class="form-control input-md"
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for="">Müşteri Email (*):</label>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <input
                    name="email"
                    type="text"
                    value="fatih@domain.com"
                    class="form-control input-md"
                    required
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for=""
                >Müşteri Cep Telefonu (*):</label
            >
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <input
                    name="gsm"
                    type="text"
                    value="5881231212"
                    class="form-control input-md"
                    required
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for=""
                >Tahsil Edilecek Tutar (TL) (**):</label
            >
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <input
                    name="amount"
                    type="text"
                    value="1000"
                    class="form-control input-md"
                    required
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for="threeD"
                >3D Secure (*):</label
            >
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <select class="form-control input-md" name="threeD">
                    <option value="true">Evet</option>
                    <option value="false">Hayır</option>
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for=""
                >Link Geçerlilik Süresi (Gün/Ay/Yıl) (*):</label
            >
            <div class="col-md-1">
                <input
                    name="expireDateDay"
                    type="text"
                    value="25"
                    class="form-control input-md"
                    required
                />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-1">
                <input
                    name="expireDateMonth"
                    type="text"
                    value="11"
                    class="form-control input-md"
                    required
                />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-1">
                <input
                    name="expireDateYear"
                    type="text"
                    value="2021"
                    class="form-control input-md"
                    required
                />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for="threeD"
                >Müşteriye Bilgilendirme Mailli Gönder (*):</label
            >
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <select class="form-control input-md" name="sendEmail">
                    <option value="true">Evet</option>
                    <option value="false">Hayır</option>
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for="threeD"
                >Komisyon Kime Yansıtılacak (Opsiyonel):</label
            >
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <select class="form-control input-md" name="commissionType">
                    <option value="1">Satıcı (Varsayılan)</option>
                    <option value="2">Müşteri</option>
                </select>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Button -->
        <div class="form-group">
            <label class="col-md-4 control-label" for=""></label>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <button type="submit" id="" name="" class="btn btn-success">
                    Ödeme Linki Oluştur
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </fieldset>
    <p>** Sipariş tutarı kuruş ayracı olmadan gönderilmelidir. Örneğin; 1 TL 100, 12 1200, 130 13000, 1.05 105, 1.2 120 olarak gönderilmelidir.</p>
</form>

<br />
<pre>
    <%= if @returnData
            JSON.pretty_generate(@returnData)
        else
            "nil"
        end
     %>
</pre>
